34c6155e69d2f195da889b0cee246e60f2649918.query:
select  (
                match_history.id,
                match_type,
                team_size,
                versus,
                rank,
                elo,
                wins,
                losses,
                win_streak)
                from player 
        INNER join player_match_history on player.id = player_id
        inner join match_history on match_history.id = match_history_id 
        where player.rl_user_id = $1
